    ----------------------------------
	RiCeBaLL
	========
	- An offline PKG installer for Picnic OS

    @deathpicnic
    ----------------------------------
	
	riceballs are must in picnic.

[+] USAGE
=========
	
	[ sudo riceball <create|install|info|clean|help> ]

	- create : creates new package spec
	- install : install created packages from spec file
	- info : displays spec file for pkg
	- clean : removes `build` dir
	- help : prints this
